    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        "They have three internals per semester, and the course B.Com is under Bangalore University. They conduct timely exams, which help in improving our studies and enable us to obtain good marks. My studies are good.",
        "The companies that came for the placement cell were some of the best companies, including big names such as HP, Amazon, Rupa Publications, and many more.",
        "Our college has excellent placement rates, with the majority of students getting selected by top companies and performing well.",
        "The fees are a little high for students coming from outside Karnataka, otherwise its good for state students studying in Karnataka.",
        "There are good hangout places within the college where you can have a good time with your friends after college, and a good canteen that provides good and hygienic food.",
        "1 lakh per year with all good facilities for washing machines will be provided. Mesh facilities are also available. There will be sharing for 2 people in one room, so there will be separate beds for each student.",
        "My college is helpful, and they are encouraging to do all programs and conduct intercollegiate athletics and feasts. All are given the opportunity to participate, and the faculties are well-educated and experienced to teach."
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        "They do take an industrial visit to show the working of big machines.",
        "Only a few students from my batch, and even from my seniors, had gotten jobs from college placement.",
        "That is the worst part in our college that needs to be improved a lot in upcoming days, although they provide good facilities in accommodation and food, the quality is the worst"
      ]
    },
